HEADWORD: Expediential
<hw>Ex*pe`di*en"tial</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>Governed by expediency;
seeking advantage; as an <xex>expediential</xex> policy.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Calculating, <xex>expediential</xex> understanding.⟦rdquo⟧
<au>Hare.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Ex*pe`di*en"tial*ly</wf> ,
<pos>adv.</pos> <au>Fitzed. Hall</au></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expediently</ent>⟦br⟧
